message.body: Are you ok? You seemed annoyed at me lady time we spoke.
Or just generally stressed? Anything I can do?
Ok cool good to hear. I'm great! This semester can't end soon enough!
Not no annoyed, just doing the school thing. How r u?
For serious! I still have soo much to do, and so little time
Same and I've conveniently stopped caring almost completely
Ha me too, I don't know when I think this shit is gettin done
I know!!! I guess I'd rather be slightly indifferent at this point. Stressing too much last semester wasn't healthy
Stress is good for no one, but I definitely stressed this semester. Horses are good, going to go see them tonight

Aw I hope you kick the stress!! And yay for horses!!! I hope you have fun with your loves. I'm practicing for the choir concert Sunday. If you need a break come check it! Should be cool & whit is performing too
Aw, I will be in balti. Going to a wedding. Which will be so fun and I won't think about school at all. Good luk tho!
